; ==================================================
; PAUSE: INSERT COMPONENTS (components)
; Z = 11.40 mm
; >> Insert the following components into their pockets:
; >>   - mcu_1
; >> Ensure all pins seat fully into their pin holes.
; >> Press the knob when done to resume printing.
